@node "Future" "Future of DelfInit"

 FUTURE


 The future of DelfInit depends strongly on end users and/or Petsoff. 
 DelfInit (as it is now) has solved most of my Delfina problems, so I am not
 especially interested in developing it further.

 If you are interested in this utility, let me know. Without your feedback 
 there will not be any new releases and new features.
@endnode

