 DelfInit 2.0 (17.07.2000)

 COMMENTS
     This second release includes new features which give users 
     greater control over the Delfina soundcard initialization process.

     Compiled with SAS/C Amiga Compiler 6.58
     Copyright © 1988-1995 SAS Institute Inc.

     Tested with Delfina Lite

     Debugged with Enforcer version 37.73 (1998-04-19)

 NEW
     * added two additional patch modes: no patching and patch all
       library functions
     * added Delfina soundcard hardware query
     * added command line options NOPATCH, STICKY and QUIET

 CHANGED
     * in order to use DelfInit as a work-a-round to "AHI killer" bug, I 
       have changed the initialization process so that DelfInit removes 
       the delfina library from memory before patching and opening the
       library
     * improvements in (error) message system

 REMOVED
     -
